name: Quick Pack Supplies
overview:
Welcome to Quick Pack Supplies, unique suppliers of a large range of packaging supplies at super affordable prices. Our most popular lines include plastic mailing bags, Grip Seal Bags and No Mixed Coin Bags.

Being based in the Midlands, UK we can ship out to the whole of the UK quickly and easily. Dedicated in bringing you the very best levels of customer support, accurate deliveries and most importantly quality packaging materials is what we do best. You have peace of mind in that all of our products are sent free of charge, no need to worry about expensive courier charges we have it covered.

Unlike many other packaging suppliers what makes us special is that were family owned, we care and have a dedication to what we do. As standard all of our parcels are sent via express services, this means you get your item within a few days not weeks.

Feel free to browse around our new website designed to bring you the customer a better and more importantly easier experience.
